HARRY: Yeah.

00:43.373 --> 00:46.003
Oh. my God.

00:53.450 --> 00:55.710
You'll excuse me.

00:58.655 --> 01:00.045
Judge Harry.

01:00.224 --> 01:01.424
Yakov.

01:01.592 --> 01:04.251
-You remember.
-Yakov Korolenko.

01:04.428 --> 01:06.688
-It's still me.
-Well. so it is.

01:06.864 --> 01:07.894
Good to see you. guy.

01:08.065 --> 01:10.025
Hey. Mac. Billie. this is Yakov.

01:10.200 --> 01:11.790
-Selma. you remember Yakov?
-Sure.

01:11.968 --> 01:15.338
Last year. he doused himself with gasoline.
threatened to blow us all up.

01:15.505 --> 01:19.165
Is this a seasonal thing.
or just an idle hobby?

01:19.342 --> 01:21.332
[LAUGHING]

01:21.878 --> 01:25.008
-I've grown since then.
-Sounds like your English has grown too.

01:25.181 --> 01:27.841
Thank you.
I go to this night school for 11 months.

01:28.017 --> 01:30.177
Nine hours a day
mastering your language...

01:30.352 --> 01:32.682
...so I can receive
all the career opportunities...

01:32.854 --> 01:36.024
-...in this free enterprise system.
-Oh. what do you do?

01:36.491 --> 01:40.161
Mop spit off floors
in Grand Central Station.

01:40.328 --> 01:43.388
God bless America.

01:43.565 --> 01:47.015
Everybody.
I want you to meet my brother Ivan.

01:47.202 --> 01:49.902
He's training dancing bear
for Leningrad Circus.

01:50.071 --> 01:51.101
Very famous in Russia.

01:51.273 --> 01:53.673
-Hi. Nice to meet you.
-Welcome to America.

01:53.842 --> 01:55.542
He doesn't speak English.

01:55.710 --> 01:59.700
And he's no rocket scientist
to begin with.

02:01.682 --> 02:03.652
So who's your other friend there?

02:03.817 --> 02:06.677
That's. uh. KGB.

02:06.854 --> 02:09.454
But act natural and laugh like:

02:09.622 --> 02:11.612
[LAUGHING]

02:17.830 --> 02:21.560
He has orders to stop Ivan
in case he wants to defect.

02:27.407 --> 02:29.637
Yakov. does your brother want to defect?

02:29.809 --> 02:31.209
You betcha.

02:37.183 --> 02:41.023
Yakov. listen.
I appreciate you thinking of me...

02:41.186 --> 02:44.646
