They hid in a coatroom.

05:45.724 --> 05:49.294
This gentleman kicked the door in.
at which point. this gentleman jumped him.

05:49.461 --> 05:51.791
I just happened to be there on a lark.
Your Honor.

05:51.964 --> 05:55.064
Bob Smith.
Smith Wholesale Circus Tent Company.

05:55.234 --> 05:57.604
-He is CIA.
