06:33.401 --> 06:34.731
Defense.

06:34.903 --> 06:38.133
Are you kidding? I barely had time
to get all these names in my pad.

06:38.306 --> 06:40.426
Your Honor.
I could be of some assistance here.

06:40.608 --> 06:42.738
Martin Glasscock.
I work for the government.

06:42.911 --> 06:45.311
-Please tell me ours.
-Ours.

06:45.480 --> 06:48.140
This is Mr. Karpov.
He's with the Soviet government.

06:48.316 --> 06:53.076
