07:37.231 --> 07:40.291
You two gentlemen come with me.
Bull. you keep an eye on everyone.

07:40.467 --> 07:42.197
Recess.

07:42.568 --> 07:44.968
You guys wanna have a seat over here.

07:45.137 --> 07:47.797
You won't let him take him back.
will you?

